said Ramirez, who has gone 48-for-164 (.293) since being recalled
from Triple-A Nashville June 19, probably will sit out until
Friday. ... The Astros have hit consecutive home runs 10 times this
season. ... Bagwell extended his hitting streak to 14 games.
