<HEADLINE> Monsanto names new board of directors  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	   ST. LOUIS (AP) - Monsanto Co., now a division of Pharmacia
Corp., announced its new board of directors Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
   Monsanto and Pharmacia &AMP; Upjohn merged earlier this year,
creating the nation's 11th largest drug company. The new company is
based in Peapack, N.J., but its agricultural business kept the
Monsanto name and headquarters here.
</P>
<P>
   Frank V. AtLee, 60, will serve as non-executive chairman of the
