senior vice president for strategy and corporate affairs;
Christopher J. Coughlin, Pharmacia's chief financial officer;
Michael Kantor, a lawyer who serves on the Pharmacia board; C.
Steven McMillan, president and CEO of Sara Lee Corp. and a
Pharmacia board member; William U. Parfet, chairman of MPI Research
LLC and a Pharmacia board member; John S. Reed, retired chairman
and CEO of Citigroup Inc. and a Pharmacia board member; and Hendrik
A. Verfaillie, Monsanto's president and CEO.
</P>
<P>
   A ninth board member will be named later, the company said.
