<HEADLINE> Tranquility Lake Wins Handicap  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   DEL MAR, Calif. (AP) -- Tranquility Lake led all the way in
winning the $136,950 Palomar Handicap by 2&AMP;frac12; lengths over Tout
Charmant at Del Mar on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
   Ridden by Eddie Delahoussaye and carrying 121 pounds,
Tranquility Lake covered 1 1-16 miles on the turf in the
