   Tout Charmant crossed the finish line 1&AMP;frac12; lengths ahead of Miss
of Wales and returned $2.20 and $2.10.
</P>
<P>
   Miss of Wales, a 24-1 long shot in the field of seven fillies
and mares, was a head in front of Spanish Fern at the wire and paid
$2.10 to show.
